node.text:
Sent a trigger to our friend Tony to let people get his take on the new CZ P-10 trigger kit. Check it out…

PC: @tony_sallis ⬅️Give A Follow
・・・
Here are the first shots through the P10F with the new @apextactical Action Enhancement Trigger kit.
.
Like most of the products they offer it was fairly simple to install. Took me about 20mins.
.
Apex claims with this kit using their disconnector you will get a sub-4lb trigger pull. That is accurate… mine consistently pulls sub-3lb 🤣
.
I haven’t done anything else to the gun except shoot it. So that was a VERY pleasant surprise!
.
The break is more of a rolling break but it is SO smooth, it does have a wall(ish) enough to know it’s there but not enough to really disrupt you if you are hosing with it.
.
I have been shooting this gun WAY more than I though honestly, the gun is just a joy to shoot and even better with this trigger in it. It is a very nice edition to an already great gun.
.
Gonna be putting some more rounds through it and maybe shoot a match with it 😎
.
The kit is available to purchase now if you want your own.
.
#apextactical #apextrigger #wdtr #apexthatczp10 #allhailtheflatty #pewpew #czp10 #czusa

node.text:
#ApexThatCZP10 with an Apex Trigger, Slide Release & Mag Release. It’s what all the cool kids are doing.

PC: @legacyarmsintl
・・・
I am really excited to be able to share a new trigger coming out in a few days by @apextactical for the @czusafirearms  P-10 series pistol, shown here installed on a P-10C. 

The P-10 is an exceptional handgun that arrived on the market in 2017 and hit the striker fired world by storm. Like many production guns… they are good… but can become great with a little work! Enter the trigger and accessory mad scientists at Apex Tactical Specialists. On Aug 17th, 2021 they will be releasing a new trigger enhancement package for the P-10 and it is everything you could hope for. 

One of my only real complaints with the stock P-10 is the over travel and slop in the factory trigger. The enhancement package removes that and also creates a nice, clean break right at 4 lbs while also reducing the reset distance. It makes for a very clean and consistent trigger pull every time. I also added the extended slide stop and extended magazine release as well and both were huge improvements over the factory OEM parts. APEX recommends having a gunsmith install the parts, but armed with a hammer, two punches and a YouTube video on full disassembly allowed me to swap out all of the parts with little effort in about 15 minutes. 

If you own one of the P-10 series pistols then I highly recommend these upgrades to turn your already great stock firearm into something noticeably better! 

Suppressor is a @rexsilentium Gen 2 SEG H suppressor in 9mm. #legacyarmsintl #czp10 #apextrigger #wdtr #apextactical #edcgear #edcupgrade #carrygun #gunsofinstagram
